---
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="font-mono text-accent-light text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">01. About me</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-6">
        A little bit<br />about myself
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Hey! I'm a 19-year-old Physics student from northern Germany with about
          7 years of coding under my belt. I work as a developer at
          <a href="https://beyondit.gmbh" target="_blank" class="text-accent-light hover:underline">BEYONDIT GmbH</a>,
          building things across the full stack.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rust is my language of choice — I love its performance guarantees and
          the way it forces you to think clearly about memory and ownership.
          On the other side, I'm equally at home crafting polished frontends,
          so fullstack is where I naturally ended up.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not writing code I'm probably buried in physics problem sets
          or poking at some new Rust crate. Feel free to reach out!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card / avatar area -->
    <div class="reveal flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative group">
        <!-- Avatar placeholder -->
        <div class="w-64 h-64 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-zinc-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 12c2.7 0 4.8-2.1 4.8-4.8S14.7 2.4 12 2.4 7.2 4.5 7.2 7.2 9.3 12 12 12zm0 2.4c-3.2 0-9.6 1.6-9.6 4.8v2.4h19.2v-2.4c0-3.2-6.4-4.8-9.6-4.8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative border offset -->
        <div class="absolute -z-10 inset-0 translate-x-3 translate-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-accent/40 group-hover:translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-y-4 transition-transform duration-300" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
